    {
      "id": "36",
      "name": "更多訊息",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "日常對話",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "「好看的牌呀...」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "七夜由美：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "「七聖召喚」，其中有些牌上的畫很好看吧，我在收集好看的牌。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "七夜由美：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "美麗，也是另外一種勝利呢！怎麽樣，要來一局「七聖召喚」嗎？",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話1：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "恭敬不如從命。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "嵐姐（玩家勝利）：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "只顧著牌面漂亮，有的時候就會非常難用...不過我是不會因此改變我的信念的，下次再打牌吧。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "嵐姐（玩家失敗）：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "用好看的牌獲得漂亮的勝利，這就是我的目標！",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話2：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "之後再說吧...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "嵐姐：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "好吧，不過妳/你要是找到什麽牌面好看的牌，記得來找我喔。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "七聖召喚",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "決鬥對局",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "關卡介紹",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "興趣是收集和使用牌面好看的卡牌，但本身的實力也不容小覷的「七聖召喚」牌手。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "【提示】這是一位強大的牌手，建議牌手等級高一些再來挑戰。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "對手陣容",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3177,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/285626729/211461a497211dfc0494d14820e78a9e_7511198725483343832.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "神里綾華",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3183,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/292125737/8eebdb1373c73b32dbf037951bd65111_217600206736086167.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "宵宮",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3188,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/285626729/a122204b72ab4c460887089b8e4664be_564022327930103633.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "菲謝爾",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "解鎖要求",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "「牌手等級」到達1級",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "獲勝獎勵",
